      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SELEC    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL'1'       WKGET
      *
     CSR         ESELEC    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CLEAR ITEM                                         *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #CLR      BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETON                     71
     C                     WRITESFLCTL
     C                     WRITESFLCTL2
     C                     SETOF                     7166
     C                     Z-ADD0         RRN     30
     C                     Z-ADD0         @RRN    40
     C                     Z-ADD0         CTRX    40
     C                     Z-ADD1         @SFRC1
      *
